{"tid":1559330,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"願榮光歸香港 好洗腦","createTime":"2019-09-10T18:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T18:28:25.000Z","uid":318876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"316ab3034c8956b13f010932d55365d4229c8f87","tid":1559330,"uid":318876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T18:27:35.000Z","msg":"讀左六年中學 ，校歌都仲未識唱。<br />\n但係依個星期，我家姐播足全日<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">願榮光歸香港</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我依家已經背到啲歌詞好熟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成日聽到啲人話聽到首歌就喊咗<br />\n雖然我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係<br />\n如果<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">願榮光歸香港</span><br />\n真係正式成為<span style=\"color: red;\">香港國歌</span><br />\n日本奧運播住佢嘅時候<br />\n我一定會感動到喊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3eba58181b0c8f7422de645208131463652daae","tid":1559330,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T18:28:25.000Z","msg":"個旋律好洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}